<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> July 21, 2025</p>

<p>Thank you for using the <strong>Aroko</strong> app. Your privacy is important to us. This app does <strong>not collect any personal data</strong> and <strong>does not connect to the internet</strong> or third-party services.</p>

<h2>What data is stored?</h2>
<p>The app only stores your game progress (like points and solved tasks) <strong>locally on your device</strong>. No data is shared online or sent to any server.</p>

<h2>Game Center and online services</h2>
<p>This app <strong>does not use Game Center</strong> or any other online services.</p>

<h2>Ads & Tracking</h2>
<p>The app is <strong>completely ad-free</strong> and includes <strong>no tracking technologies</strong>.</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, feel free to contact us:</p>
<p><strong>Email:</strong> kontakt@aroko-app.de</p>

<p>By using this app, you agree to this privacy policy.</p>

